Englehorn sails
in nine hours.
So? We gotta find Miss Darrow.

862
01:31:28,213 --> 01:31:30,841
Hey, do you hear me?
We're gonna be
stranded here.

863
01:31:32,684 --> 01:31:36,085
Miss Darrow was a great gal,
no question.

864
