Thank Mr. Baxter.

971
02:13:27,878 --> 02:13:29,846
He insisted on
a rescue mission.

972
02:13:31,181 --> 02:13:34,639
Me? I knew you'd be okay.

973
02:13:35,952 --> 02:13:38,216
That's the thing
about cockroaches.

974
02:13:38,288 --> 02:13:41,724
