back up the bowl.

976
02:13:45,228 --> 02:13:48,061
Hey, buddy?
I'm out of the bowl.

977
02:13:48,832 --> 02:13:51,494
I'm dryin' off my wings
and trekkin' across the lid.

978
02:13:59,442 --> 02:14:00,670
Driscoll!

979
02:14:02,145 --> 02:14:05,808
